# Quiz App

This is a quiz application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to take quizzes on various topics and displays the results at the end. The app provides an interactive and engaging experience for users to test their knowledge.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Demo](#demo)
- [Usage](#usage)

## Features

- Multiple-choice questions with options
- Automatic scoring and result calculation
- Display of final score and percentage
- Timer to track the quiz duration
- Easy customization of questions and options

## Demo

A live demo of the Quiz App is available [here](https://quizapp-tb.netlify.app/).

## Usage

The Quiz App can be used by anyone who wants to create and share quizzes. Here's how to get started:

1. Open the app in your web browser.
2. Enter your name and click the "Start Quiz" button to begin.
3. Read the questions and select the appropriate answer by clicking on the option.
4. Continue answering the questions until you reach the end.
5. The app will calculate your score and display the results, including the total score and percentage.
6. You can retake the quiz by clicking the "Replay Quiz" button.

